  <div class="xhr_comment_body">
    <a style="font-weight:bold" href="/user/show/26706841-steven-godin">Steven Godin</a>

      
<span id="freeTextContainer2727856791335016130"><i>Sid wrote: &quot;I&apos;m halfway through this book and enjoying the way it is written. I love the way Bolano goes off into mini-tangents, that have seemingly n</i></span>
  <span id="freeText2727856791335016130" style="display:none"><i>Sid wrote: "I'm halfway through this book and enjoying the way it is written. I love the way Bolano goes off into mini-tangents, that have seemingly nothing to do with the plot."</i><br /><br />Yes, that's one of the reasons I loved it. There is just so much to take in, and at no point, even with it being so long, did I ever find it boring.</span>
  <a data-text-id="2727856791335016130" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

    <br/>

    <span class="xhrCommentFooter greyText">
        updated
      Nov 14, 2019 01:31PM
    </span>

  </div>
